== World War I-era veterans &ndash; 7 veterans ==

Listed here are those that joined the armed services after the [[Armistice with Germany (Compi<U+00E8>gne)|Armistice]] date but before the [[Treaty of Versailles]], or where there is debate on their join-date, or whose military service is sometimes viewed as outside the scope of "WWI" but are considered WWI-era vets by the press or by their respective governments, or served in a related conflict.

